    <p>Newcastle Makerspace is at <strong>21 Gordon St, Hamilton</strong>, around the back, through the gate.</p>

    <p>The space is open irregularly, often on Wednesday evenings, or Sunday mornings.</p>
    
    <p>Meetings are announced on <a href="https://www.meetup.com/Newcastle-Makerspace-Monthly-Meetup">meetup.com</a>, the <a href="http://newcastlelug.org/mailman/listinfo/makerspace_newcastlelug.org">mailing list</a>, and via the <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/627261683965099">Facebook Group</a>.</p>


    <h2>Contact and links</h2>

    <p>
        Our main method of communication is our <a href="http://newcastlelug.org/mailman/listinfo/makerspace_newcastlelug.org">Mailing List</a>.
        Feel free to join it (usually low-volume, with sporadic bursts of activity).
    </p>

    <p>We also have a <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/627261683965099">Facebook Group</a> that we post announcements and random things to.</p>

    <p>All our codez go in our <a href="http://github.com/newcastlemakerspace" target="_blank">Github repository </a>. Pull request away!</p>

